        - `Install <install_>`_
        
        
        .. _install:
        
        Install
        -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        
        ``windtalker`` is released on PyPI, so all you need is:
        
        .. code-block:: console
        
        	$ pip install windtalker
        
        To upgrade to latest version:
        
        .. code-block:: console
        	
        	$ pip install --upgrade windtalker
